title: Art Exhibition by Paul Dyson
description: Attenborough Nature Centre will be exhibiting the art of Paul Dyson during January. The exhibition is located in the corridor at Attenborough Nature Centre and will be available during standard opening hours. A proportion of all sales will be donated to the Nottinghamshire Wildlife Trust.
